Class CreatorForConcreteClasses

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.bo2.creation.creators.CreatorForConcreteClasses
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClassCreator
public class CreatorForConcreteClasses
extends Object
implements ClassCreator

This class imitates a class creator by returning the arguments as results of its methods.
This implementation is suitable for use by production object factories in order to deal with concrete classes.
